001
002package io.vrap.rmf.base.client.error;
003
004import io.vrap.rmf.base.client.ApiHttpResponse;
005
006public class UnknownServiceException extends BaseException {
007    private static final long serialVersionUID = 0L;
008
009    public UnknownServiceException(final Throwable cause) {
010        super(cause);
011    }
012
013    public UnknownServiceException(final String message, final Throwable cause) {
014        super(message, cause);
015    }
016
017    public <T> UnknownServiceException(final ApiHttpResponse<T> httpResponse) {
018        super(httpResponse.toString());
019    }
020}
